# Cloudflare Workers Assets — headers for statically-served files (JS/CSS/img/
# font/audio) that bypass the Worker (anything not in wrangler.toml
# run_worker_first). The zone Transform Rule already sets X-Frame-Options,
# Referrer-Policy, and X-Content-Type-Options on every response, but NOT HSTS —
# the Worker only adds HSTS on the routes it handles, leaving direct-served
# assets without it. Add HSTS here so every response on this deployment carries
# it (defense-in-depth; matches the Worker's SECURITY_HEADERS value exactly).
/*
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=63072000; includeSubDomains; preload
